name: HTML Project- Innovacion 2k16
tagline: Page for a Tech-Based APaaS Startup
body:
This site was built as part of Webolve- the web design event at Innovacion 2016 at IEM, Kolkata.

It is a multi-page site, and makes use of basic HTML, CSS and bootstrap. The site has a sidebar instead of a classical horizontal navbar, and is very basic, but functional. 

It bagged the 5th place out of more than 40 teams which qualified for the finals.
